title: 'Very good Gel pen by Classmate'
body: 'Classmate Octane Gel' is a good gel type pen best for students and writers. It has a very good rubber grip and a 0.7 mm nib which works very smooth. But a very very small thing that I noticed is that it glitched sometime, but after all very gooooood pen.
